    <summary type="html">In exactly two months - April 14th - I'm doing a scalability tutorial at the MySQL conference. It'll, of course, be based on the material I've been throwing around since 2001, but once again it's greatly expanded, extended and improved! It should be lots of fun. I've yet to hear anyone tell me that they wasted their time with this particular session and I don't think people are just being polite because I'm often told that people find it tremendously...</summary>
    <author>
        <name>Ask Bjørn Hansen</name>
        <uri>http://askask.com/</uri>
    </author>
    
    <category term="conferences" label="conferences" scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#tag" />
    <category term="mysql" label="mysql" scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#tag" />
